      "message": "i did not try it, but what about an\n\n```\nif constexpr (false) {\n\tBMCWEB_LOG_DEBUG(\"...\");\n}\n```\n\n, that would rot less and not much effort to implement.\n\nIt\u0027s local to a function and does not need any extra symbol. Also relatively easy to grep for when someone needs to enable these logs.",
