      "writtenOn": "2026-02-17T02:13:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Wouldn\u0027t `BMCWEB_LOG_VERBOSE` solve both the bit rot and the code size issue?\n\nIs it really so much work to introduce that extra function.\n\nAt least then there would be a single place to patch to enable all these logs.\nAnd then later someone could spin it into a meson option / CLI argument.\n\nIf they are not useful then perhaps just delete them. But commenting out does not seem like the right solution to me.",
      "parentUuid": "77ec9ad6_72231138",
      "revId": "9e14b4bf335d6af2b94377e531e97543b5b2b731",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
